rComments: Awesome teacher! Tough grader but fair. Lectures are in depth and intriguing.

She was ok. Participate in class and you'll get on her good side. Shes alittle stingy giving A's on the papers and exams. We always covered what material we needed for the quiz right before the quiz. Shes like a double bladed sword.

this prof is awesome. she's super helpful and pretty hot too (bored in class? stare at her.) will take your calls if your phone rings. she'll help you out if you need a one-on-one, though. so i definately recommend her, really invested in the students' performance.
